              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv=\"http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/\" xmlns:lib=\"http://library.smartcampus.com/\">\r\n   <soapenv:Header/>\r\n   <soapenv:Body>\r\n      <lib:checkBookAvailability>\r\n         <bookId>CS-001</bookId>\r\n      </lib:checkBookAvailability>\r\n   </soapenv:Body>\r\n</soapenv:Envelope>",
